00:08.240 --> 00:11.680
I have not lost a second of sleep over a GMB, guys.

00:11.680 --> 00:14.080
There's three ways to get leads on Google.

00:14.080 --> 00:16.480
There's paid ads, there's the Google My Business,

00:16.480 --> 00:18.160
AKA the Maps, and there's organic.

