01:32.400 --> 01:33.840
that are ethical, that are white hat,

01:34.880 --> 01:36.240
that are above board,

01:37.120 --> 01:39.040
but don't sweat it.

01:40.240 --> 01:44.400
I've never even lost a second of sleep on this whole,

01:44.400 --> 01:46.560
everyone's in their freaking pants about this.

01:46.560 --> 01:47.680
Like, what are we going to do?

01:47.680 --> 01:48.240
